-| AC10 | `Dashboard` role is accepted but renders the Default body + HFC1023 information diagnostic (full Dashboard rendering deferred to Story 6-3) |
-| AC11 | Subtitle fetches count from `IBadgeCountService` (3-5 service) not per-type query; nullable-inject fallback renders subtitle-without-count |
