+| **D16** | **`viewKey` format matches Story 2-2 D30 byte-for-byte: `$"{boundedContext}:{typeof(T).FullName}"`.** The generator emits this once at the top of `BuildRenderTree` as a local `string viewKey`; all filter actions reference the same variable; the `data-fc-datagrid` attribute uses it. | Story 2-2 + Story 3-6 tests EXPECT this format; a different format breaks persistence round-trip. Using `typeof(T).FullName` (e.g., `"MyApp.Projections.OrdersProjection"`) ensures cross-assembly uniqueness ÔÇö two projections named `Orders` in different namespaces get different view keys. Rejected: (a) `typeof(T).Name` (short name) ÔÇö collisions across namespaces; (b) FQN + a random suffix ÔÇö breaks round-trip; (c) adopter-overridable viewKey ÔÇö over-engineering. | T1, T2; AC1, AC5 |
