+### Known Gaps (L10 discipline ÔÇö owning story linked)
+
+- **Drag-to-reorder columns in `FcColumnPrioritizer`.** Per D6, v1 presents a checkbox list ÔÇö column order within the "More columns" popover matches declaration priority. Drag-reorder UI is **Story 6-3 "Level 3 slot-level field replacement"** customization ÔÇö an adopter who wants drag-reorder writes a custom prioritizer component via Epic 6 override, or waits for Epic 6-3 if the feature reaches ubiquity.
+- **Responsive prioritizer layout for phone viewports (< 768px).** Per UX-DR7, phone variant moves "More columns" button above the DataGrid. 4-4 ships the desktop layout only. **Story 10-2 "accessibility CI gates and visual specimen verification"** is the owning story; if it lands before Epic 9-3 responsive polish, the specimen check will drive the fix.
+- **Cross-browser scroll-restore behaviour (`.scrollTop` setter nuances in Safari/WebKit).** Unit tests stub `IJSRuntime`; real-browser parity is **Story 10-2 Playwright CI** territory.
+- **Virtualize performance P99 / 100k-row adopter harness.** NFR4 gates on P95 at 500 rows. P99 tail latency + very-large-projection behaviour land in **Story 10-2 visual specimen + Epic 5 "reliable real-time experience" adopter harness**.
+- **Page-cache memory leak (`LoadedPageState.PagesByKey` grows unbounded across long sessions).** v1 ships an unbounded cache; per-view LRU eviction is **Epic 9-5 "Diataxis documentation site"** + an Epic 9-6 cleanup story (to be created before 4-4 ships, per L10). Observability (Activity spans on page fetches) is Epic 5 work.
+- **AOT/trim analyzer for `TaskCompletionSource<object>` boundary.** The Fluxor non-generic state constraint forces the cast at the dictionary boundary. **Epic 9-4 "diagnostic ID system and deprecation policy"** + an analyzer entry (new diagnostic, deferred).
+- **ICU-format plural-sensitive `PrioritizerMoreColumnsButtonLabelTemplate`.** "1 hidden" vs "0 hidden" vs "2 hidden" currently rendered as `"{0} hidden"` ÔÇö plural-neutral framing. Full ICU is **Story 9-5 "Diataxis documentation site"** ICU migration. Documented in Dev Notes T8.4.
+- **Pre-fetch / read-ahead for known-next-page.** Per scope guardrail, `GridItemsProvider<T>` fetches current page on scroll. Read-ahead is **Epic 5 "Reliable real-time experience"** territory (SignalR + optimistic fetch).
+- **Unfiltered-cap safety rail acknowledgment UI.** `FcMaxItemsCapNotice` says "use filters"; a richer flow (inline filter palette, auto-open status chips) is **Story 4.6 "empty states, field descriptions and unsupported types"** territory ÔÇö the empty-filtered-state component there is the symmetric UX surface.
+- **Boolean 3-state filter interaction with column prioritization.** Story 4-3 deferred Boolean filtering to Epic 6; if/when Boolean filters ship, their interaction with "hidden columns" needs verification ÔÇö **Story 6-3** owns.
+- **`FcNewItemIndicator` (FR21 / 3-5 follow-up) interaction with virtualization.** A new item outside the current visible page range must still be highlighted ÔÇö the indicator's implementation story needs to know `_itemKeyAccessor` exists. **Story 3-5 follow-up OR Epic 4-7.**
